    fractional parts of the cube roots of the first 64 primes (2..311).
    Returned by lookup. We do not store the constants in a global array
    because the bootstrap stage1 has limited support for static arrays of
    constants; returning by case is equivalent in cost given branch
    prediction in the SHA-256 round loop.
    @End Reasoning

